 WE CONTINUOUSLY STRIVE TO PROVIDE ATTENTIVE, PERSONAL AND EXPERT ADVICE TO ALL OUR CLIENTS
 

Established over 28 years ago by principals Seymour Zises and Andrea Tessler, Family Management is a New York-based registered investment advisor serving high net worth individuals, families and non-profit organizations. With more than $1.7 billion of assets under management, we provide attentive professional service and expert advice across all areas of financial planning.
We are privileged to have a dedicated team of experienced investment professionals who help develop a custom approach for each client based on their individual needs and investment profile. We invite you to view their profiles and background as well as the firm profile on FINRA’S BrokerCheck. We consult on a full array of financial products; including stocks, bonds, alternative investments including hedge funds, insurance products, and real estate.
